        "  - Run 'Firefox Nightly Profile Manager', choose 'Scoop-Nightly' then click 'Start Nightly'.",
        "  - Visit 'about:profiles' page in Firefox Nightly to check *DEFAULT* profile.",
        "For details: https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/profile-manager-create-remove-switch-firefox-profiles"
    ],
    "architecture": {
        "64bit": {
            "url": "https://archive.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/nightly/2026/04/2026-04-05-21-02-19-mozilla-central/firefox-151.0a1.en-US.win64.installer.exe#/dl.7z",
            "hash": "sha512:e1e95e314943f77293a0355c0985e989b9204cb769f9c5b7638f01344e10429bacbf861da97602874cc47ea1c5dc61b8f0e328aeab51dcc2faa3382d38bb7f75"
        },
        "32bit": {
            "url": "https://archive.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/nightly/2026/04/2026-04-05-21-02-19-mozilla-central/firefox-151.0a1.en-US.win32.installer.exe#/dl.7z",
